{% set title = 'LTO Network - Use case - Smart QR-codes combined with blockchain technology' %}
{% set description = 'Smart packaging solutions for product authentication and supply chain traceability' %}
{% set currentUrl = '/use-cases/track-trace-product-authentication/' %}
{% set locale = 'tr' %}

{% extends "base.njk" %}



{% block content %}

<div class="section-container">
    <section class="hero is-medium">
       <picture>
      <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/hero/hero-uc-scantrust.webp">
      <img class="overlay-image lazy" data-src="/assets/hero/hero-uc-scantrust.png" alt="Smart QR-codes">
    </picture>
        <div class="hero-body">
            <div class="container">
                <div class=""><span class="tag is-rounded is-medium blue-grey"> USE CASE </span></div>
                <h1 class="primary-text">Smart QR-codes</h1>
                <h2 class="dark-indigo">Smart packaging solutions for product authentication and supply chain traceability.</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top">
    <section class="section secondary promo-numbers-section">
        <div class="promo-numbers c use-cases">
            <div class="container use-cases">
                <div class="item use-cases">
                   <picture>
      <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/use-cases/scantrust@2x.webp">
                    <img class="promo-client lazy" data-src="/assets/use-cases/scantrust@2x.png" alt="ScanTrust">
                    </picture>
                </div>
                <div class="item use-cases">
                    <p class="promo-head use-cases">Involved parties</p>
                    <p class="promo-desc use-cases muted">ScanTrust delivers its smart QR-code services to the world's largest companies, such as ExxonMobil, Unilever, Shell, and AB InBev.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Business challenges</h2>
            <div class="columns">
                <div class="column card">
                    <picture>
            <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/polygons@2x.webp">
          <img class="card-image clip-a lazy" data-src="/assets/polygons@2x.png" alt="LTO Network - Business Challenge">
            </picture>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">Counterfeiting of QR codes on products</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">End customers do not have the tools to trust the product information presented to them to verify the goods purchased are counterfeit, damaged or misrepresented</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="column card">
                    <picture>
            <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/polygons@2x.webp">
          <img class="card-image clip-b lazy" data-src="/assets/polygons@2x.png" alt="LTO Network - Business Challenge">
            </picture>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">Collaboration between stakeholders</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">Third-party supplier or distribution partners with administrative access rights to its supply chain management system.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="column card">
                    <picture>
            <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/polygons@2x.webp">
          <img class="card-image clip-a lazy" data-src="/assets/polygons@2x.png" alt="LTO Network - Business Challenge">
            </picture>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">Integrity of supply chain systems</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">Tampering of data can often go undetected by any of the involved parties in a supply chain and therefore risk the integrity of the system</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
    <section class="section secondary">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Solution overview</h2>
            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Tamperproof QR codes</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Generating QR codes that contain a technology that is used to sign the submissions of each data entry and report being made in LTO Network to create an immutable record.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:130px;position:relative;" data-src="/assets/icons/briefcase-purple.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:130px;position:relative;" data-src="/assets/icons/notebook-purple.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Effective collaboration</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Improvement of efficiency by digitizing the paper-based processes and change in communication between the different businesses, reducing human errors when collaborating on supply chain workflows.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Data sharing</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Data that is shared by the parties involved using the systems connected to LTO Network. Stakeholders can benefit from data re-use and reduction of manual process handling.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;align-self:center;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:130px;position:relative;" data-src="/assets/icons/users-purple.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <a href="/contact/" class="button is-primary">Book a demo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>



<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Advantages using LTO Network</h2>
            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter lazy" data-bg="url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')" style="left:48px;height:250px;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:30px;top: 200px;left: 210px;" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:30px;top:-30px;left:150px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:50px;top:0px;left:-30px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:90px;position:relative; top:0px; left:73px;" data-src="/assets/icons/coins.svg" alt="LTO Network - Cost savings">
                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Cost savings</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Administrative tasks such as manual entering data into your system that receive by letter, fax, or email belongs to the past. With the blockchain technology of LTO Network, all parties can collect structured data into the systems they use to execute and administrate these processes. Working this way reduces the administrative overhead with more than 30%.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter lazy" data-bg="url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')" style="left:48px;height:250px;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:30px;top: 100px;left: -90px;" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:50px;top: 200px;left: 230px;" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:90px;position:relative; top:0px; left:73px;" data-src="/assets/icons/diagram.svg" alt="LTO Network - Easy integration">
                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Easy integration</h3>
                    <p class="muted">With LTO Network, you don't have to change your entire IT infrastructure. You can use your existing systems and application to administrate, record, and communicate on business processes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter lazy" data-bg="url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')" style="left:48px;height:250px;">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width:30px;top: 230px;left: 200px;" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="position:absolute;width: 70px;top: 9px;left: -100px;" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg" alt="LTO Network - Rock">
                    <img class="lazy" style="width:90px;position:relative; top:0px; left:73px;" data-src="/assets/icons/balance.svg" alt="LTO Network - Compliant by design">
                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Compliant by design</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Demonstrating compliance is essential in any industry. Using LTO Network you can record all data entries and steps in your business processes to safeguarding evidence and comply with the regulations. Enabling one-click compliance reporting for both internal- as external communication on your business processes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="table-container is-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="table" id="results">
                    <div class='theader'>
                        <div class="table_header dark-indigo">Theme</div>
                        <div class="table_header dark-indigo">LTO Network solution</div>
                        <div class="table_header dark-indigo">Traditional solution</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table_row">
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">Theme</div>
                            <div class="table_cell deep-lavender">Counterfeiting</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">LTO Network solution</div>
                            <div class="table_cell steel mobile-green">
                                <div class="table_icon is-hidden-mobile"> <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/table icon - good.svg" alt="LTO Network solution"></div>
                                <p>Combining Smart QR codes with blockchain makes tamperproof and trusted by the end customer.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">Traditional solution</div>
                            <div class="table_cell steel mobile-red">
                                <div class="table_icon is-hidden-mobile"> <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg" alt="Traditional solution"></div>
                                <p>Regular generated QR codes are easy to copy / counterfeit.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>



                    <div class="table_row">
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">Theme</div>
                            <div class="table_cell deep-lavender">Collaboration</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">LTO Network solution</div>
                            <div class="table_cell steel mobile-green">
                                <div class="table_icon is-hidden-mobile"> <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/table icon - good.svg" alt="LTO Network solution"></div>
                                <p>Workflow automation on business processes running between the stakeholders are automated, saving time and money. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">Traditional solution</div>
                            <div class="table_cell steel mobile-red">
                                <div class="table_icon is-hidden-mobile"> <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg" alt="Traditional solution"></div>
                                <p>Parties don't trust each other with access rights to their supply chain systems.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table_row">
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">Theme</div>
                            <div class="table_cell deep-lavender">Data sharing</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">LTO Network solution</div>
                            <div class="table_cell steel mobile-green">
                                <div class="table_icon is-hidden-mobile"> <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/table icon - good.svg" alt="LTO Network solution"></div>
                                <p>Data shared through the supply chain systems can be effortlessly and GDPR compliantly shared among multiple parties, reducing time, costs, and improving business efficiency.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table_small">
                            <div class="table_cell dark-indigo">Traditional solution</div>
                            <div class="table_cell steel mobile-red">
                                <div class="table_icon is-hidden-mobile"> <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg" alt="Traditional solution"></div>
                                <p>Paper based supply chain processes are currently emailed and subsequently processed into the system that the receiving party uses.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <a href="/contact/" class="button is-primary">
                    Book a demo
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-bottom-alt">
    <section class="section p-top-xl p-bottom-xl alt">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="columns is-centered">
                <div class="column">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="columns">
                            <div class="column is-3 card-testimonial-img">
                               <picture>
              <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/use-cases/scantrust_testimonial@2x.webp">
                                <img class="lazy" data-src="/assets/use-cases/scantrust_testimonial@2x.png">
                                </picture>
                            </div>
                            <div class="column">
                                <div class="content card-testimonial-content">
